             was indicted for <rs id="t18291203-86-off460" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18291203-86-off460" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18291203-86-off460" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18291203-86-cd461" type="crimeDate">27th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18291203-86-off460 t18291203-86-cd461"></join>, 4 iron horse-shoes, value 2s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18291203-86-victim636" type="victimName">
                  Dennis 
                  Woodin
               <interp inst="t18291203-86-victim636" type="surname" value="Woodin"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18291203-86-victim636" type="given" value="Dennis"></interp>
